    "title": "[Bugfix] Disable FlashInfer TRTLLM BF16 path for non-gated MoE",
    "user": {
      "login": "tomeras91",
      "id": 57313761,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjU3MzEzNzYx",
